sources for codex/minimax auth should include the codex cli auth, opencode auth, pi agent auth, minimax cli auth


## CLI name note

MiniMax CLI is **`mmx`** (not only a vague “minimax cli”). Discover tokens from
wherever `mmx` stores login/config (plus existing Pi/OpenCode minimax keys
already observed under `~/.pi/agent/auth.json` and OpenCode auth).